text: Nicolae Ciprian Daroczi (born 15 May 1998) is a Romanian bobsledder. He competed in the two-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of Romania Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
